<figureCitation box="[159,287,1470,1495]" captionStart="FIGURES 80 – 89" captionStartId="18.[151,264,1802,1825]" captionTargetBox="[158,1434,193,1767]" captionTargetId="figure@18.[152,1435,193,1781]" captionTargetPageId="18" captionText="FIGURES 80 – 89. Opeatocerata cylindrophallus sp. nov., holotype ♂. 80. habitus, lateral view; 81. wing apex; 82. abdomen from tergite 4 to terminalia, lateral view; 83. sternite 8, ventral view; 84. terminalia, lateral view; 85. lobes of cerci, dorsal view; 86. descendant plate of anterior cercus, posterior view; 87. subepandrial sclerite and bacilliform sclerite, dorsal view; 88. ejaculatory apodeme, phallus and hypandrium, lateral view; 89. phallus and hypandrium, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/252530/files/figure.png" pageId="17" pageNumber="519">
